end of days is a 1999 american fantasy action horror thriller film directed by peter hyams and starring arnold schwarzenegger , gabriel byrne , robin tunney , kevin pollak , rod steiger , cch pounder , and udo kier .   the film follows former new york police department detective jericho cane ( schwarzenegger ) after he saves a banker ( byrne ) from an assassin , finds himself embroiled in a religious conflict , and must protect an innocent young woman ( tunney ) who is chosen by evil forces to conceive the antichrist with satan .   the film was released by universal pictures on november 24 , 1999 .   it has grossed $ 66.9 million in north america and $ 145.1 million elsewhere , for a worldwide total of $ 212 million .   the film received mainly negative reviews .